Aloha President Kouchi, Speaker Nakamura, and Members of the Legislature:
This is to inform you that on May 19, 2026, the following bill was signed into law:
S.B. NO. 3082, S.D. 1, H.D. 1, RELATING TO MILITARY FAMILIES.
C.D. 1 ACT 013
Mahalo,
